# Caddy config for the box: a vanity redirect from the vieko.sh apex to the
# real site at vieko.dev, with the path preserved (so vieko.sh/say-no ->
# vieko.dev/say-no). Caddy auto-provisions and renews TLS via Let's Encrypt.
#
# SSH is the main event on this box (:22 -> :2222); this just keeps
# https://vieko.sh from being a dead link.
#
# Install:
#   sudo install -m0644 deploy/Caddyfile /etc/caddy/Caddyfile
#   sudo systemctl reload caddy
# Requires :80 and :443 open (see deploy/nftables.conf) for serving + ACME.

{
	email hello@vieko.dev
}

vieko.sh {
	redir https://vieko.dev{uri}
}
